rows.label: qst101802_msg001
rows.name: LIST_QST101802の仮実装

rows.label: qst101802_msg002
rows.name:
助かったも～！
物資調達中に襲われて固まってしまったも

rows.label: qst101802_msg003
rows.name:
――にしてもあれから何日も経っているし
彼女が心配で倒れちゃってるかもしれないも

rows.label: qst101802_msg004
rows.name:
傭兵団村にいるはずだから
ジゾーを彼女のところに連れてっても

rows.label: qst101802_msg0001
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Meh-meh!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0002
rows.name: Lots of food! Yummy-yummy!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0003
rows.name: Ahhhh! Tum-tum full to brim!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0004
rows.name: Should probably explain self now.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0005
rows.name:
My name Jizo, Nopon Driver!
It all thanks to you this little
Nopon was saved!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0006
rows.name:
Wandered into nasty place, full with
nasty monsters.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0007
rows.name:
Was very scared, so stayed
very still. Dust piled all over fur.
So looked like statue.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0008
rows.name:
Tum-tum got so very empty, could
not move muscle! So Jizo was
stuck here for while.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0009
rows.name:
Thank you, friends! You save Jizo
and Jizo's Blade!

rows.label: qst101802_msg0010
rows.name:
Huh? Where is...Vahsah? Vahsah!
Where Vahsah go?

rows.label: qst101802_msg0011
rows.name:
Jizo's Blade Vahsah not here...
Seem very strange.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0012
rows.name:
Maybe Vahsah gone to Hræsvelgr.
Yes, probably gone to find Jizo's
friends and get help.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0013
rows.name:
Could new friends take Jizo to
mercenary village, perhaps?

rows.label: qst101802_msg0014
rows.name:
Travel quite dangerous for little Nopon
with no Blade.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0015
rows.name: Thank you muchly.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0016
rows.name:
Haven't seen friend Possah in long,
long time.

rows.label: qst101802_msg0017
rows.name:
Jizo got a bit thinner while hungry
here, so Possah probably be surprised!
